The dataset should be organized as follows:

path/to/your/dataset/
├── images/
│   ├── image1.jpg
│   ├── image2.jpg
│   ├── ...
└── annotations/
    ├── image1.txt
    ├── image2.txt
    ├── ...


Each annotation file should contain the bounding box coordinates for each plant leaf in the corresponding image, in the format class_id x1,y1,x2,y2. For example, if an image contains two plant leaves, the corresponding annotation file might look like this:

1 10,20,100,

